00:07:47,909 --> 00:07:51,833
It means that you're trying to drive external traffic to the platform specifically.

129
00:07:51,913 --> 00:07:53,395
So again, in the example of Steam.

130
00:07:54,376 --> 00:07:56,637
you're trying to bring people to Steam,

131
00:07:57,097 --> 00:07:59,898
ideally these are people who don't even have a Steam account

132
00:08:00,138 --> 00:08:03,700
and so a very significant metric

