00:09:04,254 --> 00:09:06,816
but it just helps, I guess, to always think about

156
00:09:07,376 --> 00:09:11,898
how can I do things in my game that will help the community

157
00:09:11,978 --> 00:09:13,318
make my game more discoverable,

158
00:09:13,778 --> 00:09:16,499
and how can my discoverability feed back

