00:10:57,816 --> 00:10:59,678
but it has been around for a very long time,

193
00:10:59,738 --> 00:11:01,940
so it's by any means nothing new, but...

194
00:11:03,281 --> 00:11:07,962
I think it's still extremely valid these days and there are lots of examples of games that

