00:11:19,705 --> 00:11:24,326
something massive. So catering to a niche or a niche depending where you're from.

198
00:11:25,526 --> 00:11:33,511
To me, it means kind of thinking about game design in a relatively narrow sense and identifying

199
00:11:33,651 --> 00:11:34,992
your audience beforehand.

200
00:11:35,733 --> 00:11:40,876
This can have huge benefits, of course, because the main one is that we tap into an existing

