00:18:50,190 --> 00:18:54,633
I primarily think about content that is made in video games

315
00:18:54,733 --> 00:18:57,415
where the player has a lot of creative ownership over.

316
00:18:57,655 --> 00:19:00,597
So not necessarily, UGC is often talked about

317
00:19:00,637 --> 00:19:02,698
like a mod or a level for a game.

