00:19:02,718 --> 00:19:06,961
I'm referring to UGC as kind of creative ownership

319
00:19:07,001 --> 00:19:09,963
of content, so Minecraft, the obvious Mirror Maker,

320
00:19:10,364 --> 00:19:12,445
all the same games where you get to build your city

321
00:19:12,525 --> 00:19:14,306
or your ant colony or whatever, like they all.

