00:19:35,299 --> 00:19:37,200
So things like the Arduino,

332
00:19:37,280 --> 00:19:40,462
which is an open source electronics prototyping platform,

333
00:19:40,522 --> 00:19:42,483
and the Raspberry Pi, which is a tiny computer.

334
00:19:42,964 --> 00:19:43,844
All these things kind of...

